  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<IAbsSchedulable>, java.util.Observer, IAbsSchedulable, IComponent, IPeriodic

    public class UMPRComponent
extends AbsPeriodicSchedulable
implements IComponent, java.util.Observer
    Component bases on the UMPR model (Craveiro and Rufino, 2012); generalizes periodic resource model (Shin and Lee, 2003) and MPR model (Shin et al., 2008).
    Author:
    jcraveiro
